                    li.characteristics__item.characteristics__buttons
                        ul.characteristics__activity-list
                            li.characteristics__activity-item.characteristics__activity-buy.characteristics__activity_active
                                //- .characteristics__wr-add_active
                                .characteristics__wr-add
                                    button.characteristics__add-piece.characteristics__decrement
                                    input.characteristics__added-pieces(type="text")
                                    button.characteristics__add-piece.characteristics__increment
                                button.characteristics__button.characteristics__buy.characteristics__buy_active(type="button") Купить
                                button.characteristics__button.characteristics__in-basket(type="button") #[span В корзине] #[span перейти]
                            li.characteristics__activity-item
                                button.characteristics__button.characteristics__inform(type="button") Сообщить о поступлении
